reviewText: A story that needs to be told. Thank you.
Warning! You may die of boredom watching this movie. The only worst movie than this was "Plan 9 from Outer Space."
Good for a very, very low budget movie. A story that needs to be told, some issues with some of the acting and editing but overall it was worth it.
Really communicated the life of prisoners in the Russian Gulag. Moves slowly but worth the wait.
